data.description: Discover your slice of paradise in this stunning upgraded townhome nestled in the heart of Windsong Ranch. Step inside to find a bright and inviting open floor plan, adorned with luxurious LVP flooring and a charming stacked stone fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring exquisite quartz countertops, sleek stainless steel appliances, and abundant cabinet space.Upstairs, you'll find a delightful office nook and two spacious bedrooms, each boasting upgraded ensuites for added comfort and convenience. Retreat to your own private patio, perfect for morning coffee or evening relaxation.But the amenities don't stop there - Windsong Ranch offers a lifestyle like no other, including access to the breathtaking lagoon. With its fantastic location and unparalleled amenities, this townhome is the epitome of luxury living. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity - schedule your showing today and prepare to fall in love.
